                    "(field) lsp.CompletionItem.filterText: string?",
                    "```",
                    "",
                    "---",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "A string that should be used when filtering a set of",
                    "completion items. When `falsy` the {@link CompletionItem.label label}",
                    "is used."
